column5: Some time ago I've posted, that we have new family member .  She was 8 weeks old then, but now almost 4 months. It is time to learn something.  I like her attention to details    First "kill"     Are you talking to me    Why this stick is sooooo heavy     In winter time she will "attend"   two courses: safe boating course and net attendant Level 1  Will keep you posted

And to think you could have gotten a Lab.   I am predisposed to Labs. I have 9 at home right now. Actually the dog is kinda cute. I wish you well with it. For learning her I would suggest "clicker" training. I have had great success with that method.
